<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= product.title %></title>
  <!-- Include Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <figure class="text-center" id="newprod">
    <blockquote class="blockquote">
      <p style="font-size: 25px">PRODUCT DETAILS</p>
      <hr id="newprodline" />
    </blockquote>
  </figure>
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <img src="<%= product.imageUrl[0] %>" class="img-fluid" alt="<%= product.title %>">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h1><%= product.title %></h1>
        <p class="lead">Price: $<%= product.price %></p>
        <p>Sports products encompass a wide range of gear and equipment designed to enhance performance, safety, and enjoyment in various athletic activities. From high-performance footwear engineered for running, basketball, and soccer, to versatile apparel that wicks moisture and provides optimal comfort, these products cater to both professional athletes and recreational enthusiasts. Essential equipment such as tennis rackets, golf clubs, and baseball gloves are meticulously crafted with advanced materials to offer superior control and durability. Additionally, protective gear including helmets, shin guards, and mouthguards ensures safety during high-impact sports. Innovative fitness gadgets like smartwatches and activity trackers help monitor progress and health metrics, motivating individuals to achieve their fitness goals. Whether on the field, in the gym, or outdoors, quality sports products play a crucial role in maximizing potential and fostering a healthy, active lifestyle.</p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Add to Cart</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Include Bootstrap JS -->
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
